The master counters, safely locked inside Seċreċum Hall have finished counting all the votes. People anxiously try to anticipate the result by reading the expressions on the master counters' faces as they stream out onto the balcony to proclaim that YOU have won the election and are now the next Chieftain of the Qrifuwi.

 

-50% Jewelry -50% Gems

 

-75% Fur -50% Leather

 

The Qrifuwi don't like snakes. That is not altogether unusual, but also they do not like eels. Worms, frogs, fish, anything that was not raised in direct sunshine is condiered by the Qrifuwi to be dirty. Much prefering dry food, anything mushy or shiny is considered to be suitable only for animals and the very poorest of society to consume.

-50% Fish -50% Oil

 

Guide your people to prosperity. Go forth into the world.
Welcome, Atalaster. Leader of the Qrifuwi.
